<br>
Cant say for sure about the effect of the mask, but the pet definitely used the belt, and it was fun to watch it tank woodland lions and young kodiaks on its own in EC <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  250hp is a lot at that level...<br>
<br>
However after a while the pet started to behave strange, it would just keep standing in one place and not follow me anymore. This finally got me killed as my pet would not come to my aid.<br>
<br>
When I got back I still saw it stand there, now rogue (indifferent con). Made a new pet, gave it belt and mask again and killed the old pet - got no exp though.<br>
<br>
But new pet again started to stand around only, so I decided to finish that session. Dont know if it was the belt/mask that caused trouble, or if the game was somehow else buggy.<br>
<br>
